WEBVTT

00:00.020 --> 00:01.843
<i>Previously on</i> "Bates Motel"...

00:01.892 --> 00:05.454
We pulled two bodies out of
falls lake a couple days ago.

00:05.578 --> 00:07.118
We just identified one of them.

00:07.176 --> 00:09.344
I thought you'd want to be
the one to tell your wife.

00:09.643 --> 00:11.338
<i>The Bates Motel
is a family business,</i>

00:11.405 --> 00:13.365
<i>and I feel like
I've been part of the family.</i>

00:13.445 --> 00:16.478
N-Norma, you've always been
so close to me.

00:16.590 --> 00:17.790
<i>He killed his mother.</i>

00:17.877 --> 00:18.971
<i>He loved her.</i>

00:19.034 --> 00:20.265
If you know what Norman's done,

00:20.289 --> 00:21.364
you're an accessory to murder.

00:21.388 --> 00:23.422
Says the escaped convict.

00:30.986 --> 00:32.533
<i>Norman Bates,
you're under arrest</i>

00:32.598 --> 00:34.354
<i>for the murder of Sam Loomis.</i>

00:34.418 --> 00:36.213
<i>Norman, I'm gonna
get you a lawyer.</i>

00:36.262 --> 00:38.947
Don't say anything until
your lawyer gets there.

00:39.465 --> 00:41.174
<i>Norman is not a bad person,</i>

00:41.261 --> 00:42.459
and he's not a criminal.

00:42.507 --> 00:43.867
What do I need
to know about him?

00:43.911 --> 00:45.369
He has another side to him.

00:45.410 --> 00:46.439
<i>I don't know what you'd call it.</i>

00:46.463 --> 00:48.697
<i>Maybe multiple personalities.</i>

00:50.084 --> 00:52.947
I'm the only one
who's gonna protect you.

00:55.658 --> 00:58.635
<i>It's time for me to fix this.</i>

01:01.774 --> 01:03.404
Turn to your left, please.

01:06.299 --> 01:08.244
Okay, if you could
step up to the desk, please.

01:08.309 --> 01:10.306
I need to take your prints.

01:10.728 --> 01:12.650
Wha... what do I do here?

01:12.804 --> 01:15.213
Place your right thumb
down on the scanner.

01:15.263 --> 01:17.244
Hold it there
until you hear a beep,

01:17.385 --> 01:18.799
and don't move.

01:19.251 --> 01:20.644
There's no ink?

01:20.708 --> 01:22.828
Ink smudges.
Everything's gone digital.

01:22.900 --> 01:24.635
Wait for the beep.

01:25.947 --> 01:30.084
Place your right index finger
on the scanner, please.

01:32.025 --> 01:34.192
Left thumb, please.

01:34.334 --> 01:35.783
So what happens next?

01:35.841 --> 01:38.174
- Wait for the beep.
- Oh, right.

01:39.697 --> 01:41.757
Tomorrow you'll
go before the judge.

01:41.822 --> 01:43.674
After that,
it's anybody's guess.

01:43.839 --> 01:46.439
Mine is you'll be
moved within 48 hours

01:46.504 --> 01:48.596
to a pre-trial
detention facility.

01:48.721 --> 01:50.353
Left index finger, please.

01:50.407 --> 01:52.645
Detention facility?
You mean, like, prison?

01:53.072 --> 01:55.736
You'll be warehoused wherever
the judge wants to keep you.

01:55.908 --> 01:57.994
But it won't be here.
We don't do that.

01:58.096 --> 02:00.064
That's a bit premature.

02:00.228 --> 02:02.033
Whatever happened to bail?

02:02.213 --> 02:03.613
That's up to the judge.

02:03.801 --> 02:04.901
Personally,

02:04.989 --> 02:06.744
I wouldn't count on it.

02:06.925 --> 02:10.360
♪♪

02:10.384 --> 02:14.096
♪♪

02:16.000 --> 02:22.074
