02:33.944 --> 02:36.144
Dylan, what happened?

02:43.116 --> 02:45.084
Katie's with my dad.

02:45.420 --> 02:47.230
I'm with you,
we'll figure it out.

02:47.381 --> 02:50.572
I wanted to be here
and help you with this.

02:57.372 --> 02:59.891
Em... Emma,

03:01.820 --> 03:03.430
I don't know
how to tell you this.

03:03.515 --> 03:07.414
♪♪

03:08.211 --> 03:10.414
They, um, th... they
found your mom's body

03:10.470 --> 03:12.953
up in Falls Lake.

03:13.689 --> 03:15.899
She was murdered.

03:17.337 --> 03:19.567
I... I know it was Norman.

03:19.831 --> 03:23.688
♪♪

03:23.712 --> 03:27.563
♪♪

03:36.855 --> 03:38.655
I'm sorry.

03:41.397 --> 03:42.883
I'm sorry.

03:57.246 --> 03:59.995
