♪♪

04:11.793 --> 04:13.793
♪♪

04:13.879 --> 04:17.629
<i>♪ Call me irresponsible ♪</i>

04:17.745 --> 04:21.027
<i>♪ call me unreliable ♪</i>

04:21.096 --> 04:25.496
<i>♪ throw in undependable too ♪</i>

04:25.675 --> 04:28.752
♪♪

04:28.939 --> 04:30.020
<i>♪ Do my foolish alibis... ♪</i>

04:31.798 --> 04:33.178
You catching a cold?

04:33.298 --> 04:34.970
No, it's dust allergies.

04:35.130 --> 04:36.440
This place probably
hadn't been dusted

04:36.464 --> 04:37.492
since the mother died.

04:37.524 --> 04:38.793
She died two years ago,

04:38.853 --> 04:40.978
but this room looks like
she still lives here.

04:41.061 --> 04:42.505
It's like a museum.

04:42.907 --> 04:44.214
Yeah, maybe.

04:44.353 --> 04:46.103
Pretty interactive museum.

04:46.204 --> 04:47.290
<i>♪ Unpredictable ♪</i>

04:47.337 --> 04:49.860
someone's been
sleeping in the bed.

04:50.478 --> 04:51.796
Pulp's still fresh.

04:51.939 --> 04:53.695
<i>♪ Rainbows ♪</i>

04:53.798 --> 04:59.506
<i>♪ I'm inclined to pursue ♪</i>

04:59.634 --> 05:03.384
<i>♪ call me irresponsible ♪</i>

05:03.464 --> 05:07.364
<i>♪ yes, I'm unreliable ♪</i>

05:07.430 --> 05:11.657
<i>♪ but it's undeniably true ♪</i>

05:11.739 --> 05:13.939
