17:21.980 --> 17:25.705
♪♪

17:25.730 --> 17:29.573
♪♪

18:18.435 --> 18:20.029
I'm so sorry, Norma.

18:20.205 --> 18:23.966
♪♪

18:23.990 --> 18:27.622
♪♪

18:31.583 --> 18:33.591
I miss you.

18:33.822 --> 18:37.216
♪♪

