I understand.

30:44.066 --> 30:47.635
♪♪

30:48.838 --> 30:50.393
Emma?

30:50.682 --> 30:53.283
I don't know.
I don't know, Dylan.

30:53.854 --> 30:55.154
Let's not talk now.

30:55.345 --> 30:59.174
♪♪

30:59.291 --> 31:02.908
♪♪

31:10.855 --> 31:12.410
You're leaving now?

31:12.925 --> 31:14.410
Yeah.

31:15.000 --> 31:17.500
Yeah, I'm gonna go home
where it's normal.

31:18.550 --> 31:20.995
Okay.

31:43.156 --> 31:44.602
Bye.

