Can I help you?

32:10.193 --> 32:12.779
I'm here to see Norman Bates.

32:14.339 --> 32:16.576
Just wait here a moment.

32:18.888 --> 32:22.459
Um, there's someone
here to see Norman Bates.

32:22.811 --> 32:25.811
♪♪ <i>Somber orchestration...</i>

32:26.033 --> 32:29.771
♪♪

32:29.873 --> 32:33.365
♪♪

32:40.414 --> 32:43.929
♪♪

32:43.953 --> 32:47.750
♪♪

33:09.559 --> 33:11.082
Hello, Emma.

33:12.707 --> 33:14.981
I guess I know why you're here.

33:15.754 --> 33:17.481
You do?

33:18.036 --> 33:20.348
Because I'm not sure I do.

33:21.254 --> 33:24.223
Well, it's about
your mother, I imagine.

33:25.137 --> 33:27.169
They think I killed her.

33:27.450 --> 33:29.328
I think you did too, Norman.

33:29.450 --> 33:33.153
♪♪

33:33.715 --> 33:36.707
No, I wouldn't kill anybody,
Emma.

33:38.207 --> 33:40.348
You know that.

33:40.817 --> 33:42.629
It's me,

33:43.247 --> 33:44.942
Norman.

33:45.403 --> 33:47.372
Your Norman, your friend.

33:47.481 --> 33:50.129
♪♪ <i>Eerie music...</i>

33:50.283 --> 33:54.004
♪♪

33:54.098 --> 33:57.965
♪♪

33:59.926 --> 34:01.520
Where's Norman?

34:01.692 --> 34:04.293
♪♪

34:04.379 --> 34:06.613
♪♪

34:06.762 --> 34:08.973
I am sorry about
your mother, Emma.

34:11.206 --> 34:12.706
She wasn't nice.

34:12.873 --> 34:15.402
She was using Norman
and she was using you.

34:15.481 --> 34:16.840
She didn't deserve to die.

34:16.956 --> 34:18.411
Death isn't about deserving.

34:18.473 --> 34:20.942
It's just part of the deal.

34:22.114 --> 34:23.418
She made her own bed.

34:23.496 --> 34:26.887
You... you know that
better than anyone.

34:27.762 --> 34:30.402
Can I talk to Norman?

34:31.567 --> 34:33.989
Well, Norman's sleeping.

34:34.692 --> 34:36.036
In his room.

34:36.270 --> 34:38.197
♪♪

34:38.496 --> 34:41.167
There's an apple pie
in the oven.

34:41.309 --> 34:43.456
And when he wakes up,
he'll smell it baking

34:43.536 --> 34:45.270
and know that everything's okay.

34:45.426 --> 34:48.184
♪♪

34:48.340 --> 34:50.949
♪♪

34:51.308 --> 34:53.465
Well, can you tell him
something for me?

34:53.606 --> 34:57.051
♪♪

34:57.207 --> 34:58.903
Can you tell him
that I miss him?

34:59.004 --> 35:02.864
♪♪

35:02.958 --> 35:06.676
♪♪

35:11.126 --> 35:14.778
♪♪

35:16.809 --> 35:20.473
♪♪

35:29.452 --> 35:30.969
Easy, easy, easy.

35:31.072 --> 35:32.100
Easy.

35:32.215 --> 35:33.633
♪♪ <i>Brooding orchestration...</i>

35:33.683 --> 35:36.047
Sorry to drag you into this.

35:36.359 --> 35:37.813
What do you want, Alex?

35:37.922 --> 35:40.102
Norman Bates.
Let's go.

35:41.221 --> 35:44.941
♪♪

35:45.674 --> 35:48.050
- Hey, couldn't stay away, huh?
- Get 'em up.

35:48.145 --> 35:50.245
Up.
Get 'em up.

35:50.450 --> 35:52.680
Get in there.
Go, go.

35:53.108 --> 35:56.800
♪♪

35:57.200 --> 35:58.800
Open it.

36:01.301 --> 36:02.808
Nobody move.
Nobody move.

36:02.910 --> 36:05.210
Up, up, up, hands up, now.
Hands up.

36:05.439 --> 36:07.371
Get up.
And get in the back.

36:07.465 --> 36:08.819
- What the hell is this, Romero?
- Get in the back.

36:08.843 --> 36:10.004
Shut up and get in the back.

36:10.058 --> 36:11.510
♪♪

36:11.574 --> 36:13.233
Okay, on the floor, face down,
hands on your heads.

36:13.257 --> 36:14.340
Let's go, everybody.

36:14.380 --> 36:16.285
Let's go... you too, Davis,
let's go.

36:16.425 --> 36:17.555
I never saw him coming.

36:17.684 --> 36:18.785
No talking!

36:18.863 --> 36:20.066
Where's your sheriff?

36:20.220 --> 36:21.293
Uh...

36:21.455 --> 36:22.715
Where's your sheriff, Miller?

36:22.850 --> 36:24.610
Uh, she's in...
She's in the field.

36:24.658 --> 36:26.043
- Is there anyone else here?
- No.

36:26.203 --> 36:27.941
Okay, collect their firearms.

36:28.021 --> 36:29.752
Nice and easy,
thumb and forefinger only.

36:29.777 --> 36:31.246
Slide them over to me.
Let's go.

36:31.367 --> 36:33.636
♪♪

36:33.731 --> 36:36.136
♪♪

36:36.436 --> 36:37.941
Let's go.

36:38.088 --> 36:39.455
Slide it over.

36:39.715 --> 36:41.207
Next one.

36:41.375 --> 36:42.808
Throw that one in the trash.

36:42.957 --> 36:44.933
♪♪ <i>Dark orchestration...</i>

36:45.027 --> 36:46.043
Let's go.

36:46.111 --> 36:47.211
What do you want, Rmero?

36:47.236 --> 36:48.496
I want you to shut the hell up.

36:48.552 --> 36:49.568
He's here for Norman Bates.

36:49.592 --> 36:51.808
What did I just say?
What did I just say?

36:53.220 --> 36:54.582
Get 'em up.
Get 'em up.

36:57.162 --> 36:58.411
♪♪ <i>Suspenseful dramatic music...</i>

36:58.435 --> 36:59.559
On your feet!

36:59.699 --> 37:00.918
Everyone up!

37:00.980 --> 37:02.996
Move into my office now!
Go!

37:03.089 --> 37:05.819
♪♪

37:05.879 --> 37:07.246
Stay tight.

37:07.334 --> 37:11.152
♪♪

37:11.729 --> 37:13.402
I said, "Tight."
Tight.

37:13.499 --> 37:15.136
♪♪

37:16.643 --> 37:18.308
Up, keep 'em up.

37:18.545 --> 37:20.293
Wait, hey, what...
What's happening?

37:20.447 --> 37:22.543
♪♪ <i>Brooding music...</i>

37:22.662 --> 37:23.662
Hello, Norman.

37:23.750 --> 37:24.750
Open it, open it.

37:24.808 --> 37:26.418
What's he doing here?

37:27.305 --> 37:29.922
In, everyone in.
